metadata.name: Beyond
metadata.description:
By defining the undefined, we can enter the vastness and go beyond boundaries into the limitless.

About the Series -
The Circle is a universal symbol with extensive meaning. It represents the notion of totality, wholeness, original perfection, eternity, timelessness, all cyclic movement & God.

The series is about understanding the essence of us all in & as the collective & the idea of interbeing & shared space. Interbeing are guidelines for anyone wishing to live mindfully.

Series : Circle of togetherness
